parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbag not deploying in an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light appears on the dashboard
the airbag sensor is not functioning properly
the passenger side airbag light is off or intermittent
and the seat belt chime is not working.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger presence sensor can cause the airbag to not deploy in an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The passenger side airbag light is off or intermittent
the airbag sensor is not functioning properly
and the seat belt chime is not working.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause the airbag system to malfunction, which can result in the airbag not deploying in an accident, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light appears on the dashboard
and the wiring harness needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag and electrical system can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries. The electrical system failure can also cause the vehicle to stall or shut down, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: lights and radio not turning off when the car is turned off

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition and starter system can cause the engine to stall or die while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: engine restarts and travels for various distances before occurring again
refusal to turn over or take a jump.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery and electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: refusal to turn over or take a jump

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the voice command system can cause driver distraction and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Voice command system not working properly
volume periodically takes off with increasing loudness uncontrollably.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective headlamps can cause impaired visibility, reducing the light output and potentially leading to accidents, especially during nighttime driving or in low-visibility conditions.
symptoms: water builds up inside the headlight assembly due to condensation
the headlight is foggy with moisture
